{"type":"message","id":"746ff8f9","parentId":"21877f8a","timestamp":"2026-05-03T07:01:12.353Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Sun 2026-05-03 03:00 EDT] Write a dream diary entry from these memory fragments:\n\n- Weather Cache Cron: Running every 15 minutes (3:28 AM start); All updates successful\n- Status: 8:43 AM - systems running normally; Morning Brief cron at 5:30 AM\n- Status: 11:13 AM - weather cache cron running, all good; 2:28 PM - weather cache updated, all systems running; Car wash check cron should have fired at 2:00 PM (14:00Z)\n- Video Content Idea (Bobby's - 5:10 PM): **Concept:** AI videos modeled after Minute to Win It game show; **Format:** Short, high-stakes 60-second challenges; **Goal:** Viral hooks, audience retention, views; **Storytelling approach:** IMPACT FIRST — hook in first 3 seconds with t\n- Video Content Idea (Bobby's - 5:10 PM): Think of it like: show the crazy finish first, then reveal how you got there\n- 3 AM Dreaming - Apr 18: MC watchdog ran clean; All overnight weather cache updates complete; Apr 17 was a quiet day - Bobby didn't respond to Affirm reminders; Affirm $15.31 still past due (since Apr 17 9 AM)\n- Day Summary: Morning Brief 5:30 AM ✅ (delivered via Telegram); 7 AM Check-In ✅ (sent: Affirm T-Mobile $18 due TODAY, Earth Day tomorrow, Apr 27 $424.41); Midday Check-In 12 PM ✅ (sent: today + tomorrow + Apr 27 reminders); Evening Wrap-Up 5 PM ✅ (sent via Telegram)\n- Active Project: Recipe Rip: Bobby is actively developing Recipe Rip with Cody; Check-in cron jobs timing out (need timeout bump from 120s to 300s)\n- 10:26 AM Status: Morning brief delivered 5:35 AM; Morning check-in sent 8:26 AM; Affirm $15.31 payment reminder sent at 8:56 AM (4 min before due); Past due reminder sent 9:11 AM\n- Worked extensively on `~/Desktop/OpenClaw-Guide-By-Bobby/styles/cover-style1-trust.html` (cover page design). Final approved Mac version is the current `cover-style1-trust.html`. Guide work is paused for now.; Created copies during guide testing:; `cover-style1-trust-MAC.html`; `"}],"timestamp":1777791672289}}
